{"tid":1293912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每一個今日在場嘅記者都應該投訴啲狗","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:53:20.000Z","uid":197468,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bac370a0c7e5ac6f9cd29a2a41e8faccdff651bc","tid":1293912,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"佢只要有試過擋開你嘅鏡頭嘅話你就已經可以投訴<br />\nd狗依家連記者都唔識尊重咁點解你地要尊重佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察通例第39章 警察與市民和傳播媒介的關係<br />\n<br />\n39-05  如何配合傳媒工作<br />\n<br />\n              在事發現場的人員，須：<br />\n<br />\n              a) <span style=\"color: red;\">以互諒互讓的態度，盡量配合傳媒工作；以及</span><br />\n<br />\n              b) <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不應妨礙傳媒的攝錄工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo039.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo039.pdf&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=bd751e2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo039.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"0b91eaea75df202e1d94cf09d55ddf14f406bf29","tid":1293912,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"be10151456661753f199be83f32e818876fb41a8","tid":1293912,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"頹"},{"pid":"e8492cfc43ac8fd505648cb3f8b9919d67623ef6","tid":1293912,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1e22d083dab8867a89d74385dbc8b826cc48630e","tid":1293912,"uid":274798,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:11:00.000Z","msg":"仲可以向邊度投訴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />監警會唔柒理，又唔成立獨立調查小組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知仲可以點投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif